"title": "9314: resurrection, of the dead",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9314: resurrection, of the dead",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture speaks of a general resurrection of all people at the end of time, which will be followed by judgment.</p>\n<h2>The resurrection of the dead predicted</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28-John5:29\">JHN 5:28–5:29</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The resurrection of the dead will occur at Jesus Christ's return</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12-Rev20:13\">REV 20:12–20:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:52\">1CO 15:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16\">1TH 4:16</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection of the dead includes both the righteous and wicked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:15\">ACT 24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:32\">MAT 25:31–25:32</a></p>\n<h2>Attitudes to the resurrection of the dead</h2>\n<h3>Denial by false teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:12\">1CO 15:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:23\">MAT 22:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:18\">MRK 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:27\">LUK 20:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:8\">ACT 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Ridicule from unbelievers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:18\">ACT 17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:32\">ACT 17:32</a></p>\n<h3>Unbelief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:8\">ACT 26:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29-Matt22:32\">MAT 22:29–22:32</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:24-Mark12:27\">MRK 12:24–12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:34-Luke20:38\">LUK 20:34–20:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:35-1Cor15:44\">1CO 15:35–15:44</a></p>",
